<Author>MemberfromPadova
<Content>Consistently good and satisfactory NH Belagua is a business oriented hotel located 500 m off the Avenida Diagonal and 200 m away - 10 min walk - from the closest subway stop (Fontana).The hotel is in a residential part of the district of Gracia, thus not very central. On the other side, the location is relatively quiet. Rooms are no frills, but perfectly adequate, very clean and comfortable. Staff is corteous and helpful.I have use this hotel a few times and I have always been very satisfied despite being a bit off track from where life is. But as long as you travel for business, I think this is a good choice, also in view of a very good value for money. 
